Sentencas: High-performance solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) is in urgent need of high-quality electrolyte powders with high reactivity and chemical uniformity.
Titulo: Modified room temperature solid-state synthesis of yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) nano-powders for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Here, 8 mol% Y2O3 doped ZrO2 (YSZ) nano-powders were synthesized by an improved solid-state reaction method at ambient temperature, and were applied to the fabrication of SOFC electrolytes.
Titulo: Modified room temperature solid-state synthesis of yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) nano-powders for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: YSZ nano-powders show average grain sizes of similar to 20 nm and high dispersibility, which is comparable with or even better than some other chemical methods.
Titulo: Modified room temperature solid-state synthesis of yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) nano-powders for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Benefitting from their high reactivity, dense YSZ electrolytes (relative density of 97.9%) can be obtained at a relatively low sintering temperature of 1400 degrees C.
Titulo: Modified room temperature solid-state synthesis of yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) nano-powders for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The optimized electrical conductivity reaches up to a high value of 0.034 S/cm at 800 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Modified room temperature solid-state synthesis of yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) nano-powders for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The anode supported single cell with the construction of Ni-YSZ/YSZ/Sm0.2Ce0.8O2-delta(SDC)/La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3-delta (LSCF) exhibits the peak power density of 0.827 W/cm(2) at 800 degrees C while taking wet H-2 as fuels and ambient air as oxidants.
Titulo: Modified room temperature solid-state synthesis of yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) nano-powders for solid oxide fuel cells
